# BuildTwin Frontend — Definition of Done

See also: `.cursor/rules/sprint-implementation.mdc` | `../BuildTwin/docs/SPRINT-WORKFLOW.md`

Do **not** mark a task complete until all applicable checks pass:

## Frontend

- `npm run lint` — ESLint zero errors
- `npm test -- --run` — Vitest unit + component tests green
- `npm run build` — production build compiles (same step as Docker build)
- Mapper/date logic: use `parseDateOnly()` for API `YYYY-MM-DD` strings

## User-facing features

- `npm run test:e2e` — Playwright demo mode (when UI behavior changed)

## Honest status

Report: code done / tests pass / lint pass / build pass / E2E pass — separately.
